Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:43.59,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll get to \Nsee the fall next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is the light for the early sleepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and stars are \Nlight for the night owls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Complete all the rituals by night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The night of Yule comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.29,Default,Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, beloved child of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.63,Default,Straight Bangs Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,Human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.52,Default,Straight Bangs Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be \Ndone preparing for Yule?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.22,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yule?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.84,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,We're preparing for Yule soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:24.79,Default,Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,You sleepy-head, the night will \Nbe here before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.87,Default,Straight Bangs Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,Set the Yule Log ablaze in your hearth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.85,Default,Alien Angel,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Horned God and\Nhis Dark Lady walk the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:35.82,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:36.63,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:42.78,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.65,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.49,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Yule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:51.15,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I call them the Yule twins because they \Nalways come on the day of the winter solstice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.06,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't really know their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.35,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.19,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.16,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,You have to tell me if you get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.35,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.38,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.05,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure of a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.48,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help Chise when she's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.15,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He's been like this ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.70,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,What's even the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.37,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:27.28,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,You understand Chise far \Nbetter than I do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:32.98,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,It may be tough for you to say anything \Nbecause Chise tends to hide things,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.90,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,but you can tell me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.31,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.39,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,This is painfully awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.81,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bit cold right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.74,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.20,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we just came inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.57,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.79,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Let's prepare for Yule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.70,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.32,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Is this "pretty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.21,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.64,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.66,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,They say that traditionally, it's okay \Nto kiss under the mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.16,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.78,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.38,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.02,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.88,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Could you crouch for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.14,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.54,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,And back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.19,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.36,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,How to phrase it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.78,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,My back? My waist? They feel tingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.44,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.53,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.52,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,One for you too, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.85,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.78,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sir, I'll be sure to deliver this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.14,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's always so last-minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.72,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.26,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, I left a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.30,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.85,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, I'll be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.23,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.41,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you all the way out to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.38,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.98,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas present, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.87,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,For Renfred-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.39,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.51,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know what to get for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.90,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What did you get him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.46,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Before, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:27.22,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one giving me gifts, so I thought\N this year, I'd get him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.32,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,They're really digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.77,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting that bonehead anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.73,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.80,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never even thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.96,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for a present together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.65,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.88,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,She's not giving me a choice, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.99,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.54,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,There's the question of taste, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.02,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.98,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what his tastes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.12,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.86,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I've never given anyone a gift before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:38.36,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... well, I don't know too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.01,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.81,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone like that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.94,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same boat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.64,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,In the same boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.32,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,You're a mage and I'm a sorcerer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.32,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,but we both live our lives \Nstudying with our masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.99,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,So we're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.07,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:05.13,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:11.27,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the lady from \NMr. Ainsworth's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.76,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Hazel-san. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:16.77,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.93,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:30.13,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike mages, sorcerers don't notice \Npeople like us, who've disguised ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.50,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:45.02,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas presents, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.28,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.85,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,What about something that \Nyou can picture them using?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:01.44,Default,Hojack Borseman,0000,0000,0000,,Think really carefully about them. \NImagine something that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.17,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take another lap around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.18,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.89,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Something he uses all the time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.09,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.52,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.30,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You can't copy me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.07,Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.15,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:31.67,Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.34,Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out, like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.32,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing drugs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:39.71,Default,Hoodie,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.61,Default,Hair,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.54,Default,Hair,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where the hell did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.56,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.58,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.20,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,They're just stragglers from my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.12,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Alice-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.03,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Do drugs taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.25,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.38,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,They're not my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.14,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't start by choice, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.34,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,It's still like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.84,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fun to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.73,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.32,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.29,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:53.50,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,My shitty parents got me into drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:58.78,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I had nothing going for me outside of selling\N that crap, when Master took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.99,Magus-Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen the blonde brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.72,Magus-Flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,We need to teach her a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.12,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.35,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.27,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to stay here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.26,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.90,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.18,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mikhail Renfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.22,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,Call me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.72,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.56,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.68,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:41.32,Magus-Internal/narrator,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't trust him in \Nthe slightest at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.87,Magus-Internal/narrator,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I'd grown up in a trash pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:51.24,Magus-Internal/narrator,Human,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way I could trust people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.84,Magus-Internal/narrator,Human,0000,0000,0000,,But, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.13,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.23,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.18,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to open them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.86,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:43.68,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was my fault, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.26,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:50.77,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.49,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.92,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.39,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.72,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.40,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.45,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be getting yourself hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.02,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.75,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to treating wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.94,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.20,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'm self-taught, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.32,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.09,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:44.85,Magus-Flashback,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, as your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.35,Magus-Flashback,Small face,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.11,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about that makes me feel like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.82,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.83,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.79,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to think anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.60,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide for myself whether \NI'm happy or miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.01,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for hearing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.62,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:29.91,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:40.42,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, is my servant bird at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.64,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,It's this tiny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.64,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.34,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write you a letter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.39,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming out at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.31,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.69,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it works out for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.45,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,You have a friend now. I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.52,Default,Human,0000,0000,0000,,As my big brother, do you approve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:11.47,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.77,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.16,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Stella! Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.25,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.88,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.87,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.68,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want all the way out in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.21,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,And you even met with\N Renfred's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.45,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:51.35,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many times \Nyou've put yourself in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.22,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sneak out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.42,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.14,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.74,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.63,Default,Daww,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too angry, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:03.72,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.76,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,This is angry? I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.15,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.64,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:12.56,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.98,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I went to buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.46,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a day early, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.91,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.09,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.01,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd get me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.56,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.32,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:38.73,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:43.08,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You're always wearing the same one, \Nso I thought maybe it relaxes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.04,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.19,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.69,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,One for you, too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.84,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.41,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I've only made them for \NAngelica and her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.30,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd make one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.20,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.32,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.03,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:25.44,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica told me a long time ago that \Nshe wanted a teddy bear as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.59,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I think this year's is my best one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:33.03,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing it ever since?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.21,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.50,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.31,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.62,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,It has a bit of a trick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.75,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.84,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all gifts for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.91,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica, Simon, and Lindel \Nhave gotten you gifts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.65,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts are meant to be \Nopened on Christmas Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.87,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,so these are for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.12,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.64,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have dinner first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.44,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll scold you after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:08.69,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping he'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.30,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me.\N I would have gone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.46,Default,Edgelord,0000,0000,0000,,And I could have gotten some shopping done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.10,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:23.88,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I had a secret talk with another \Ngirl about girl stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:47.58,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what Christmas\N is supposed to be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:54.57,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm looking \Nforward to waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.02,Default,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.08,Default,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I see a pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:58.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient being, Ashen Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:02.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Siblings that are at the \Nmercy of his eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:06.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The mage and the girl \Nlend them a hand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:09.36,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back! He's {\i1}my{\i0} brother!
